# Script 1: Precision Clocks
# Display synchronized time points and clock precision across a city
# Connects to nearest airport (NTP) for authoritative time
# Shows time synchronization quality as heatmap overlay

airport Munich
sync to IANA timezone Europe/Berlin
sync to NTP server time.nist.gov

# Query precision points across city
precision map within 2km radius
show clock network
show synchronization quality as heatmap

# Display results
time show
clocks show
precision report
